description:
Recently sold: $398,900. Main Level
* Beautiful open foyer is a warm welcome to any guest.
* Gourmet kitchen features granite countertops, elegant wood cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, dramatic tile backsplash, tiered breakfast bar, plate rack, walk-in pantry, recessed and pendant lighting.
* Dinette area with abundant natural light and decorative pillars. Open floor plan.
* Elegant formal dining room boasts amazing recessed ceiling, archways, and pillars. 
* Living room features stunning floor-to-ceiling stone gas fireplace with custom mantel and lighted art niche.  Impressive wall of windows brings the outdoors in.
* Master bedroom features recessed ceiling with detailed millwork, ceiling fan, large walk-in closet, and tranquil pond views.  Luxurious master bath with tile flooring, double sink vanities, granite countertops, linen closet, window, tile surround whirlpool tub and shower.
* Secondary bedroom could also function as an office. Spacious closet with mirrored doors.
* Attractive full bath with extraordinary tile flooring and bath/shower area, window, and granite countertops.
* Laundry/Mud room includes sink, plentiful cabinets, closet, granite countertops, and garage entry door.
Lower Level
* Spacious family room with walkout to backyard and patio.
* Adjacent wet bar offers tiered bar area with granite countertops, sink, grand tile backsplash, plentiful cabinet space, wine rack?perfect for entertaining.
* Exercise/craft/sitting room with mirrors and recessed lighting.
* Remarkable sauna includes separate shower area and adjustable benches.
* Secondary bedrooms with so much to offer.
* 3/4 bath with tile floor and shower area.
Additional
* Main level maintenance free deck, lower level patio, and front porch.
* Durable steel siding.
* Newer hot water heater.
* Alarm system.
* Installed RedLINK thermostat for comfort.
* Neutral quality window blinds/treatments throughout. 
All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed.
